  • Method Details

    • createBooking

      void createBooking(int userId, int gymId, int transactionId, String bookingDate, String bookingTimeSlot, String bookingType, int bookingAmount)
      Creates a booking with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      userId - The ID of the user making the booking.
      gymId - The ID of the gym being booked.
      transactionId - The ID of the transaction associated with the booking.
      bookingDate - The date of the booking.
      bookingTimeSlot - The time slot of the booking.
      bookingType - The type of the booking (e.g., online, in-person).
      bookingAmount - The amount charged for the booking.

    • bookSlots

      Returns:

      Throws:
      BookingFailedException - if viewing the bookings fails.

    • makePayment

      int makePayment(int userId, String paymentDetails, String expiryDate, String modeOfPayment) throws BookingFailedException
      Makes a payment for a booking.
      Parameters:
      userId - The ID of the user making the payment.
      paymentDetails - The payment details.
      expiryDate - The expiry date of the payment method.
      modeOfPayment - The mode of payment (e.g., credit card, debit card).
      Returns:
      The transaction ID of the payment.
      Throws:
      BookingFailedException - if the payment fails.
